dct_title_s: Carte de la Nouvelle Angleterre, Nouvelle Yorck, et Pensilvanie
dct_description_sm: Par M. B. Ing. de la Mar.
Bar scale in lower French miles.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
"Tom. XIV. in 40. no. 9." in lower left.
Shows New England from central Pennsylvania to southern New Hampshire.
